Contains logic which computes and proposes a weight schedule

protocol.name: Weigh Children Under 5 Years Old Every Month

meta.documentation: For a quantity observation, indicates wether the observed value is expressed in imperial pounds
Ensures that a weight observation is expressed in kilograms, converting from pounds if required

fact.name: Patient Is Underweight
fact.csharp: ((double)context["Observed Weight Expressed in Kgs"]) < (double)context.DataSets["#org.santedb.cdss.weight.zscores"].Lookup("gender", context["Record Target Gender"]).Lookup("age", context["Record Target Age in Days"]).Select("zMinus2")

fact.name: Patient Is Overweight
fact.csharp: ((double)context["Observed Weight Expressed in Kgs"]) > (double)context.DataSets["#org.santedb.cdss.weight.zscores"].Lookup("gender", context["Record Target Gender"]).Lookup("age", context["Record Target Age in Days"]).Select("zPlus2")

rule.name: When Patient Is Underweight Set Interpretation to Low and propose vitamin supplement

raise.issue: Patient weight is abnormally low - Please provide appropriate nutritional counseling and check for conditions such as ringworm, vitamin supplement.

rule.name: When Patient Is Overweight Set Interpretation to High and Inform Clinician

raise.issue: Patient abnormally high - Please provide appropriate nutritional counseling
